casebody.data:
No.-.

Mas et al., Plaintiffs and Appellants, v. Borinquen Sugar Company, Defendant and Respondent. Decided October 6, 1913. Messrs. Aponte & Aponte for appellants-Messrs. Alvarez Nava and Dominguez for respondent.

Appeal from the District Court of Humaoao. Motion of appellant for leave to withdraw his appeal. Motion denied because of failure to show in any way the date of the judgment appealed from and of the filing of the appeal.
